<collectingCountry box="[1041,1134,1344,1370]" name="Canada" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Canada</collectingCountry>
, and in the United States from Maine south to North Carolina. Although it is widespread it is infrequently collected at black light
</materialsCitation>
